cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper deals with processing techniques for robust reconstruction of motion properties in dynamic environments, which involves computer vision (CV) and robotics (RO) concepts. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.RO are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves mathematical modeling and analysis, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (LG), artificial intelligence (AI), and systems and control (SY).
